title: REWARDS
body: **Am i the ONLY one that hasnt gotten my rewards yet...i am gold 5 and just wanted the maokai skin... **

replies.body: Nope, a few players have reported that they haven't received it yet.  We're [not finished rolling out rewards](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/page/2016-ranked-season-ends-soon), so anyone missing stuff will be getting their goodies.  Don't worry, they're still coming!
